{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
How [A]long before I get in?[Em]
Before it starts, before I begin?[D]
How [A]long before you decide?[Em]
Before I know what it feels like?[D]
Where [A]to, where do I go?[Em]
If you never try, then you'll never know[D]
How [A]long do I have to climb[Em]
Up on the side of this mountain of mine?[D]
{end_of_verse}


