{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
[D] Look [A]up, I look up at night[Em]
Planets are moving at the speed of light[D]
Climb [A]up, up in the trees[Em]
Every chance that you get
Is a chance you seize[D]
How [A]long am I gonna [Em]stand
With my head stuck under the sand?[D]
I'll [A]start before I can stop[Em]
Before I see things the right way up[D]
{end_of_verse}


